{"type": "article", "id": 63823, "title": "这个用拉伸材料做的头盔，还能帮你呼叫救护车｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-16T23:05:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 1277, "name": "IKEA"}, {"id": 58614, "name": "Takt"}, {"id": 27979, "name": "PearsonLloyd"}, {"id": 48673, "name": "Coil + Drift"}, {"id": 48062, "name": "Offecct"}, {"id": 8926, "name": "Tom Dixon"}, {"id": 58615, "name": "David Trubridge"}, {"id": 58616, "name": "Lukas Franz"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190516201910Sw6mIah4GtAZbOTy.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 16.2px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 19.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 392.0px; line-height: 29.0px; font: 21.3px Avenir; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 29.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #3c3c3c; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #3c3c3c} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #3c3c3c; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #3c3c3c} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Madillo helmet by Lukas Franz </h3><p>Madillo 头盔是 2018 年 iF Design Talent Award 的获奖作品，出自设计师 Lukas Franz 之手。第一眼看上去，Madillo 头盔在形式和功能上都具有破坏性，它与你过去看到的任何头盔完全不同。</p><p>设计师采用了一种定向拉伸材料，这种材料和不寻常的图案使 Madillo 能够舒适地包裹你的头部形状。其中空的格栅式设计还允许光线穿过其裂缝，使 Madillo 能够作为指示器工作。一个薄的照明模块位于外部材料下方，闪烁灯指示用户何时向左或向右转动。这个功能可以让驾车司机知道你的目标。</p><p>此外，Madillo 还带有救生灯，点亮头盔以吸引路人的注意力。它甚至可以将 SOS 信号发送到最近的医院并召唤救护车，同时传送用户的位置以确保被护送到安全地点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201956aGxiKuX5VelO42Tn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201956QUI4T7CHkzNgm2Ku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201957SPov4jKnLku0HZB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201957LzkrWgjS9E3AnDwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201957x9yifmeBA754sJIn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201958r8BEhKpFAvdRWNz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201958SVX6Dtr0s49WCOi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516201958saHpDITu57CNf2iR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2019/05/15/the-madillo-helmets-design-allows-it-to-work-as-an-indicator-and-distress-beacon/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Waka by Offecct &amp; David Trubridge</h3><p>设计师 David Trubridge 在与瑞典家具品牌 Offecct 的第二次合作中设计了新品 Waka，它可以作为一个休息空间，也可以是休闲会议、沟通的空间。</p><p>Waka 的灵感源自船型结构，David Trubridge 赋予了座椅一个看起来像漂浮物的轮廓，好似漂流起来一般。</p><p>它有一个有趣的形状，可能会让人们停下来弄清楚它是什么或如何使用它，然后意识到它正在对你微笑。Waka 有 3 米长，中间较宽，向两端逐渐收窄，允许多人同时坐在上面。其绗缝软垫外观采用交叉影线图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202149E2TyX5RQbcrfKt9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202149mzvwKaYs9A8U20qE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202150sXSwQglkc75fuix0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202150XamzGUwfp96BRH1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202151M4stjkCTEN0Vebch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202150AxuYtBqc50iIsdzX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/david-trubridge-designs-waka-as-a-place-to-rest-for-offecct/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Assemblage by Coil + Drift</h3><p>本月 NYCxDesign 期间，纽约布鲁克林设计工作室 Coil + Drift 开设了一个临时展厅，推出其新系列产品 Assemblage。</p><p>展厅将展出完整的 Assemblage 系列照明产品，搭配 Coil + Drift 现有系列的家具，配有全新饰面。当创始人兼设计师 John Sorensen-Jolink 为他的第一个家设计定制照明产品时，Assemblage 系列已经有了雏形，它非常适合照亮高高的空间。之后，Sorensen-Jolink 决定将设计变成一个完整的系列，包括 Yama 台灯，Toam 系列和 Pierce 系列，具有丰富的形状和质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202252HtrwZkGsPIEFTRei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713580\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202252I5BeTKnmvC4F81dS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905162022525E29stWFMZorARjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202253vjcUQX6BJ50xe3sD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905162022537EzJeYNTUjdg4y1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202254YEAzFJZxtn5fkVBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.261728\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202254X1qp5k8G09s4Yw6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202255LW5huyibGIc7Rx0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202255NaohHXQjt3sC5Kki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.841975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202255yHgwKvmP0oY6rGCq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.coilanddrift.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coil + Drift</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cross Chair by PearsonLloyd for Takt</h3><p>伦敦工作室 PearsonLloyd 最近为哥本哈根新兴设计品牌 Takt 设计了一款平板式家具 Cross 椅子，将便利性、经济性与优质材料结合在一起。</p><p>Cross 椅子以交叉结构命名，四条椅腿搭配胶合板座椅和靠背，结构本身由实心橡木制成，给人一种非扁平包装、高品质椅子的感觉。</p><p>PearsonLloyd 表示，这款“坚固而轻便”的木质椅子的设计理念是“价格合理，不影响质量或对环境产生不利影响” 。</p><p>椅子以可回收的扁平包装盒的形式交付，包括四个拆卸的木材模块，带有六个螺钉。</p><p>“我们希望找到一种能够以直接，可理解的方式传达装配原理的设计，” PearsonLloyd 创始人 Tom Lloyd 解释道。“两个交叉构件重叠的方式受到了酒盒中插入物的启发。很明显，它们以某种方式结合在一起，这意味着几乎不需要任何装配说明。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202357m2eBUEbkO3vxupzI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799915\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202357q8IA3isnpEV4fOFP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202358tR45m0AqSjf9eWl6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202358yjJab1AnLeHCM9O4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.456430\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202359lhzaOAkjDmRZWVvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202401xwAy8FW1qkSM0Uh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905162024015ucqagJKBWfNlXd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516202402n84qElDbh3UmPeY5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://pearsonlloyd.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PearsonLloyd</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Gardening Will Save The World by Tom Dixon + IKEA</h3><p>在 5 月 21 日即将开幕的切尔西花卉展览会上，英国设计师 Tom Dixon 和宜家合作将带来一个城市农业试验园。</p><p>该花园旨在展示人们可以采用的方法，在家里种植食物，同时减少食物浪费，并通过传统知识和最新的技术创新传达园艺的美丽和功能重要性。</p><p> “园艺将拯救世界”分为两个层次：凸起的花园，让游客沉浸在植物绿洲中，包括树冠，花卉和植物的树冠状生态系统; 和基地花园，一个园艺实验室，实施水培技术，种植超天然食物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516203502ZT435KYMjSHF8J0A.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657226\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516203503E2JgzudfYhIHTL1y.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.423759\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516203503AMV6rFnqm410HxDP.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.776900\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516203503U4YOKHx9cXW6I3Do.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190516203504ygQKtepAra9sZqGd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.115000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}